summary:
Development expert with experience in: gender, reproductive health and aids, governance, natural ressources management, 

My ambition is to contribute to a more even distribution of development opportunities in the world, while preserving the planet. My passion is to open space for all people to develop and organize themselves. I am convinced that opening space for diversity and selforganisation is the most effective way to innovation and finding creative solutions for the problems the world is currently facing.

Specialties: Open Space Facilitation
Storytelling
Organisational Change strategies
Textwriting
Knowledge development
